    ns1:inpersonHours "36 horas (46.2%)"@es ;
    ns1:numberOfCredits 3.0 ;
    ns1:otherInformation """Some information on Sustainable Developments Goals of Nanoelectronics will be given in this module, in particular SDG3, 7, 9 and 11.
A debate on the intensification of these modules (3 ECTS given in 8 weeks, instead of 15-16 weeks) is suggested among the coordinators and students. On one side, this pocedure allows a better organisation for the students, with a lower number of modules at the same time; on the other hand, they don¿t have enough time to think and assimilate the new information and the new knowledge."""@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Junio"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Febrero"@es ;
    ns1:teachingPeriod "2025-26" ;
    ns1:teachingPeriodMonths "Febrero-Junio"@es ;
    ns1:totalHours "36 horas"@es ;
    schema:activitiesWorkload "100%"@es ;
    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description """The students should achieve advanced knowledge on materials, structures and devices used in nanotechnology, especially in nanoelectronics and micro/nanosystems, for applications in sensors and actuators used in information technology and communications, bioengineering, etc.
A cooperative and participative methodology will be used."""@es ;
    schema:director <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/fernando.calle%40upm.es> ;
    schema:inLanguage "Inglés"@es ;
    schema:instructor <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/fernando.calle%40upm.es>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/j.pedros%40upm.es> ;
    schema:name "Nanoelectronics"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/CB09> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CB09" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sepan comunicar sus conclusiones y los conocimientos y razones últimas que las sustentan a públicos especializados y no especializados de un modo claro y sin ambigüedades/ Students are capable of clearly and unambiguously communicating their conclusions, and the underlying knowledge and rationale to specialist and non"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/CE1> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE1" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Capacidad para aplicar los fundamentos científicos del comportamiento físico y químico de los materiales para relacionar causalmente sus propiedades fundamentales físicas y químicas con su comportamiento macroscópico y el de los productos con ellos realizados / Ability to apply the scientific foundations of the physical and chemical behavior of materials to correlate their fundamental physical and chemical properties with their macroscopic behavior and that of the products made with them."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/CE7> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CE7" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Manejo de herramientas de simulación numérica para diseño y análisis de materiales, desde la escala microscópica a la macroscópica / Management of numerical simulation tools for design and analysis of materials, from the microscopic to the macroscopic scale"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/CG1> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG1" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Uso de la lengua inglesa: Los alumnos son capaces de transmitir conocimientos y expresar ideas y argumentos de manera clara, rigurosa y convincente, tanto de forma oral como escrita, adaptándose a las características de la situación y de la audiencia / Use of the English Language: Students are able to transmit knowledge and express ideas and arguments in a clear, rigorous and convincing manner, both orally and in writing, adapting to the characteristics of the situation and the audience ."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/CG3> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG3" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Trabajo en equipo: Los alumnos desarrollan la capacidad para trabajar en equipo, integrarse y colaborar de forma activa en la consecución de objetivos comunes / Teamwork: Students develop the ability to work as a team, integrate and actively collaborate in achieving common goals."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/CG5> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG5" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Organización y planificación: Los estudiantes son capaces de fijar objetivos, con la planificación y programación de actividades (tiempo y fases) y con la organización y gestión de los recursos necesarios para alcanzarlos / Organization and Planning: Students are capable of setting objectives, with the planning and programming of activities (time and phases) and with the organization and management of the necessary resources to achieve them.."@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/CG9> a ns1:Competency ;
    ns1:competencyCode "CG9" ;
    ns1:competencyDescription "Que los estudiantes sepan comunicar sus conclusiones y los conocimientos y razones últimas que las sustentan a públicos especializados y no especializados de un modo claro y sin ambigüedades/ Students are capable of clearly and unambiguously communicating their conclusions, and the underlying knowledge and rationale to specialist and non"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/RA1> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA1" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "Saber comunicar conocimientos, procedimientos, resultados o técnicas relacionadas con el comportamiento y el uso de materiales"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/RA11> a ns1:LearningResult ;
    ns1:learningResultCode "RA11" ;
    ns1:learningResultDescription "knowledge of the basic fabrication methods, structure and properties of nanomaterials and other forms of nanostructured hybrids"@es .

<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/43000619/2025-26/RA4> a ns1:LearningResult ;
